  "industry_note": "ZTA (Zirconia-Toughened Alumina, 10-20% ZrO₂ dispersion in α-Al₂O₃ matrix). Y-PSZ 입자가 alumina matrix 안에서 stress field 받아 tetragonal → monoclinic transformation → crack 흡수. ρ 4.1 / σf 700 / E 350 / KIC 6 (alumina 의 1.3× — toughening). Tmax 1500°C (over T 시 zirconia overaging). Mohs 9. 가공 비싸 ($150+/kg). 의료 hip joint head/ball (CeramTec BIOLOX delta 가 ZTA + Cr/Sr 추가), wear-resistant component (pump, valve), 정밀 ball valve seat."
